{"tid":1069593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"主持教育會議 習命洗腦「從娃娃抓起」","createTime":"2019-03-20T05:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T06:40:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cd9ef10da0e52ab6a6baa86563ccca0a2ee091d1","tid":1069593,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T05:30:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190320/20637049\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190320%2F20637049&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9CVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=833c9a40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190320%2F20637049&h=76b382a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190320/20637049</a><br />\n<br />\n主持教育會議 習命洗腦「從娃娃抓起」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190320/large/20ch105p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190320%2Flarge%2F20ch105p.jpg&h=9a8c2460&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n習近平前日主持召開學校思政課座談會。新華社<br />\n<br />\n習近平治下的中共越來越左。3月18日習在北京主持一個「學校思想政治理論課教師座談會」，指出必須培養「一代又一代擁護中共領導和中國社會主義制度的人才」，並強調洗腦要「從學校抓起、從娃娃抓起」。「在這個根本問題上，必須旗幟鮮明、毫不含糊」。這是習首次召集大學、中學、小學思政課教師代表座談。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190320/large/20ch104p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190320%2Flarge%2F20ch104p.jpg&h=8df73023&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地一名教師給學生們講國徽的知識。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推動思政課建設<br />\n<br />\n此次會議規格不低；除習之外中央分管意識形態的常委王滬寧，主掌思政課的中辦主任丁薛祥皆有出席。 習近平會上稱，要引導學生「扣好人生第一粒扣子」；要「傳導主流意識形態，直面各種錯誤觀點和思潮」，要求學校黨委書記、校長要帶頭推動思政課建設；各地各部門負責人「要積極到學校去講思政課」。會上被安排發言的教師來自各地，涵蓋大學退休教授到現職教授，乃至中學、小學的思政課教師。<br />\n<br />\n有消息指，剛閉幕的全國政協大會曾發表一份專題調研報告，稱在傳播馬列主義過程中，部份思政課教師對當今社會一些問題避而不談，導致無法對青年學生思想「及時引領」；甚至一些大、中學校講台上，有思政課老師向學生傳播非主流的意識形態，被舉報後遭校方處分。內地的大、中、小學及研究生課程都開有思想政治課，2016年起已統一更名為「道德與法治」。<br />\n<br />\n多維網  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n粉絲1,600萬 賣廣告盛惠94萬<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n「六四酒案」開審前突換辯方律師"},{"pid":"430d6fc46d5260db6b61425952af5e63b3ae183d","tid":1069593,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T05:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.wenming.cn/web_wenming/images/jswmjs20180822-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.wenming.cn%2Fweb_wenming%2Fimages%2Fjswmjs20180822-2.jpg&h=10414cc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/2DA681D2-900D-4A68-93FA-F6E3CE4D0638_w650_r0_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2F2DA681D2-900D-4A68-93FA-F6E3CE4D0638_w650_r0_s.jpg&h=485a048d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1415c0cd6d465235ae1ff896084d5b73826ce719","tid":1069593,"uid":1989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"430d6fc46d5260db6b61425952af5e63b3ae183d","tid":1069593,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T05:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.wenming.cn/web_wenming/images/jswmjs20180822-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.wenming.cn%2Fweb_wenming%2Fimages%2Fjswmjs20180822-2.jpg&h=10414cc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/2DA681D2-900D-4A68-93FA-F6E3CE4D0638_w650_r0_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2F2DA681D2-900D-4A68-93FA-F6E3CE4D0638_w650_r0_s.jpg&h=485a048d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T06:11:08.000Z","msg":"幼稚園聽定小學內容都冇咩所謂既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7469ad71f5705ac74b12a0989b7d1f7e91f9720d","tid":1069593,"uid":100276,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T06:14:54.000Z","msg":"習種條仆街連細路都唔放過，要支那一代傳一代出班賤人出嚟"},{"pid":"258e64bbf205f8c4a72befd6559e4ee9017038a8","tid":1069593,"uid":127569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T06:15:54.000Z","msg":"爹親娘親不及習主席親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"052b8c71c2302b6e0d7fb7634287e397404583e1","tid":1069593,"uid":179409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T06:40:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">2016年起已統一更名為「道德與法治」。</span><br />\n支國法治，即係當權者用法律整治人民，即係人治。"}]}